    "description": "Hanatour Japan Co., Ltd. provides travel arrangement services in Japan, South Korea, China, and internationally. It operates through Travel Business, Bus Business, Hotel and Other Facility Management Business, and Other segments. The company arranges inbound travel services from South Korea, China, and Southeast Asia. It is also involved in the arrangement of local hotels, restaurants, and buses; provision of made-to-order planned products, such as travel incentives and package tours; online arrangement and sale of accommodation-only products for hotels and Japanese inns; organization and planning of tours for Korean wave events; arrangement of tickets for business trips overseas and within Japan; sale of made-to-order arranged travel products for company trips; arrangement of bus tours around the country; operation of a shuttle bus service; and Korean visa application support services. In addition, the company operates chartered tour buses mainly for inbound tourists; provides development and marketing consultancy, and business dealings services; operates hotels; and engages in software and web system development, operation, and maintenance management services. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan. Hanatour Japan Co., Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Hanatour Service Inc."
